  4. SIGNIFICANT BUSINESS PROCESS EXCEPTION
================================================================================

The Workflow Service Restriction in Section 3 does NOT apply when workflow
provisioning is a component of a Significant Business Process (Section 1.7),
not the primary product itself.

Examples of permitted use under this exception:

- A credit scoring platform using workflows to orchestrate scoring pipelines.
- An IoT monitoring platform routing sensor data through workflows.
- A payment processing system managing transaction routing via workflows.
- An insurance underwriting system orchestrating risk assessment.
- An e-commerce platform managing order fulfillment via workflows.
- A healthcare integration platform connecting hospital systems.

In each case, the product delivers substantial domain-specific value beyond
workflow execution. The workflow engine is an implementation detail.


